    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. When you say \"instability and unpredictable demand\" for the second area, are you implying that the demographic shifts—specifically the changing racial and cultural makeup of the neighborhood—are a primary driver of that risk? How much weight should an investor put on those specific demographic changes when calculating long-term stability?",
