    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I see. You mentioned that different groups have different expectations for maintenance and community investment. Can you be more specific about which demographics tend to be more \"stable\" investors versus those that might pose a risk to property values? Like, if we're looking at a shift toward more diverse or immigrant populations, does that statistically correlate to a higher risk of neighborhood decline in your analysis?",
